[{"title":"C 語言入門","url":"/posts/c43bd37.html","content":"<img src=\"/posts/c43bd37/C.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"開始之前\"><a href=\"#開始之前\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"開始之前\"></a>開始之前</h2><blockquote>\n<p>PS：內容適用於初學者，若有程式基礎的可跳過！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>先到<a href=\"https://sourceforge.net/projects/orwelldevcpp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Dev C++</a>下載編譯器，並安裝。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"程式碼基本架構\"><a href=\"#程式碼基本架構\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"程式碼基本架構\"></a>程式碼基本架構</h2><figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 引用函式庫</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;stdlib.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 程式主體</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//..........</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//..........</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"變數\"><a href=\"#變數\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"變數\"></a>變數</h2><ul>\n<li>整數型態 (int, long, long long)<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 變數宣告</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> a;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">long</span> b;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"keyword\">long</span> c;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>浮點數型態 (float, double, long double)<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 變數宣告</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">float</span> a;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">double</span> b;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"keyword\">double</span> c;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>字元型態 (char)<code>PS:在C裡頭字串是字元陣列</code><figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 變數宣告</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">char</span> a;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"陣列\"><a href=\"#陣列\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"陣列\"></a>陣列</h2><ul>\n<li>差異<br>變數:取一個空間存放一個變數。<br>陣列:取一個連續空間放很多個整數。</li>\n<li>用法<ul>\n<li>整數型態<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 陣列宣告</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> arr[長度];</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>浮點數<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 陣列宣告</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">float</span> arr[長度];</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>字元<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 陣列宣告</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">char</span> arr[長度];</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>PS：宣告陣列時請記得要告知長度為何，否則要使用動態配置記憶體(malloc()函數)。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"printf-scanf-印出-儲存\"><a href=\"#printf-scanf-印出-儲存\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"printf/scanf 印出/儲存\"></a>printf/scanf 印出/儲存</h2><ul>\n<li>於螢幕上印出程式結果 (printf)<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%d\"</span>, 變數);  <span class=\"comment\">// 印出整數型態 (int)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%ld\"</span>, 變數);  <span class=\"comment\">// 印出長整數型態 (long)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%f\"</span>, 變數);  <span class=\"comment\">// 印出浮點數型態 (float)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%lf\"</span>, 變數);  <span class=\"comment\">// 印出雙精度浮點數型態 (double)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%c\"</span>, 變數);  <span class=\"comment\">// 印出字元型態 (char)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>將輸入儲存到變數中 (scanf)<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">scanf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%d\"</span>, &amp;變數);  <span class=\"comment\">// 儲存整數型態 (int)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">scanf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%ld\"</span>, &amp;變數);  <span class=\"comment\">// 儲存長整數型態 (long int)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">scanf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%f\"</span>, &amp;變數);  <span class=\"comment\">// 儲存浮點數型態 (float)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">scanf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%lf\"</span>, &amp;變數);  <span class=\"comment\">// 儲存雙精度浮點數型態 (double)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">scanf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%c\"</span>, &amp;變數);  <span class=\"comment\">// 儲存字元型態 (char)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"if-else-條件判斷\"><a href=\"#if-else-條件判斷\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"if/else 條件判斷\"></a>if/else 條件判斷</h2><ul>\n<li>條件判斷，顧名思義當條件為真時，才進行if/else內的程式碼；反之跳過。<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(條件式)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// 程式碼</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//..........</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//..........</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// 程式碼</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//..........</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//..........</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>巢狀式<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(條件式)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(條件式)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"comment\">// 程式碼</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//..........</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//..........</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"comment\">// 程式碼</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//..........</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">//..........</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// 程式碼</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//..........</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//..........</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"switch-case-條件判斷\"><a href=\"#switch-case-條件判斷\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"switch/case 條件判斷\"></a>switch/case 條件判斷</h2><ul>\n<li>與if/else相同功能，視情況做使用。</li>\n<li>用法<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">switch</span>(變數或運算式)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">case</span> 符合的數字或字元:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t<span class=\"comment\">// 程式碼</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">case</span> 符合的數字或字元:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t<span class=\"comment\">// 程式碼</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">/* .</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">           .</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">           .</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">           .</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">        */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">default</span>:  <span class=\"comment\">//當不符合其他的例子時才做執行(可省略)。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t<span class=\"comment\">// 程式碼</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"for-while-迴圈\"><a href=\"#for-while-迴圈\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"for/while 迴圈\"></a>for/while 迴圈</h2><ul>\n<li>迴圈目的:執行相同程式碼多次</li>\n<li>for<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 次數總共5次</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;i &lt; <span class=\"number\">5</span>;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// 要執行的程式碼</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// .............</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// .............</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>PS：遞增 { 變數++ } 、 遞減 { 變數– }</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>while<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 當條件成立時繼續執行，反之跳出。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(條件式)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// 要執行的程式碼</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// .............</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// .............</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>do while<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 當條件成立時繼續執行，反之跳出。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 與while不同，至少會執行一次。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 最後才進行判斷</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">do</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">// 要執行的程式碼</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// .............</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// .............</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;<span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(條件式)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>PS：使用while或do-while時，要注意條件判斷，否則可能會造成無窮迴圈。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"指標\"><a href=\"#指標\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"指標\"></a>指標</h2><blockquote>\n<p>PS：偏難，建議先熟練基礎語法再學。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"待補\"><a href=\"#待補\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"待補\"></a><strong>待補</strong></h2><h2 id=\"其他\"><a href=\"#其他\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"其他\"></a>其他</h2><p>如果覺得自己已經熟練語法，可以試試去<a href=\"https://onlinejudge.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">UVA</a>挑戰題目。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"參考\"><a href=\"#參考\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"參考\"></a>參考</h2><p>參考網址:<a href=\"https://openhome.cc/Gossip/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">良葛格學習筆記</a></p>\n","categories":["程式語言","C/C++"],"tags":["C","Program for beginner","Computer science"]},{"title":"Hexo 與 Gitpage","url":"/posts/7c1d345c.html","content":"<img src=\"/posts/7c1d345c/HEXO.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#前言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前言\"></a>前言</h2><p>這是我第一次使用Gitpage / hexo / Node.js架設靜態前端網站，<br>所以我想說其中一篇文章就拿來寫hexo的教學，給尚未嘗試過的人做參考。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"開始之前\"><a href=\"#開始之前\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"開始之前\"></a>開始之前</h2><ul>\n<li><p>安裝<br>請先到<a href=\"https://git-scm.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Git</a>、<a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Node.js</a>進行安裝。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Github 申請帳號<br>前往<a href=\"https://github.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Github</a>網站進行帳號申請。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>打開 git bash 設定資料</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>設定自己的名字和信箱</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git config --global user.name &quot;名字&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ git config --global user.email &quot;信箱&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><code>可使用 git config --list 查看資料</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>設定ssh</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ ssh-keygen</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><code>詳細操作請至下方點選連結！</code></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"hexo-安裝\"><a href=\"#hexo-安裝\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo 安裝\"></a>hexo 安裝</h2><p><code>PS:下述皆使用git bash教學。</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>請建立一個資料夾存放你的網站資料  <figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkdir Blog\t\t&#x2F;&#x2F;建立Blog資料夾</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>開啟 git bash</li>\n<li>hexo 安裝  <figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-cli -g\t&#x2F;&#x2F;安裝hexo</span><br><span class=\"line\">cd Blog&#x2F;\t&#x2F;&#x2F;切換目錄到Blog</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo init\t&#x2F;&#x2F;初始化hexo</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo server\t&#x2F;&#x2F;啟動伺服器(可使用網頁輸入localhost:4000查看)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>hexo 指令<br>  可至官網<a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-tw/docs/commands\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hexo</a>查看其餘指令。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"hexo-部署\"><a href=\"#hexo-部署\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo 部署\"></a>hexo 部署</h2><ul>\n<li>請先於github新增檔案儲存庫</li>\n<li>安裝  <figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li>部署  <figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo generate\t&#x2F;&#x2F;產生靜態資料</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo deploy\t&#x2F;&#x2F;部署至github</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"hexo-主題\"><a href=\"#hexo-主題\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo 主題\"></a>hexo 主題</h2><ul>\n<li>可到<a href=\"https://hexo.io/themes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hexo主題</a>挑選自己喜歡的。</li>\n<li>我使用的為NexT主題，下述皆以NexT主題教學。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"hexo-設置\"><a href=\"#hexo-設置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo 設置\"></a>hexo 設置</h2><hr>\n<h2 id=\"參考\"><a href=\"#參考\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"參考\"></a>參考</h2><ul>\n<li>參考網址<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/twtrubiks/Git-Tutorials\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">twtrubiks/Git-Tutorials</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.jaycetyle.com/2018/02/github-ssh/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Jayce’s Shared Memory</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://ithelp.ithome.com.tw/articles/10207725\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo - 前端也能建置部落格！安裝與建置篇 - iT 邦幫忙::一起幫忙解決難題，拯救 IT 人的一天</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://ithelp.ithome.com.tw/articles/10208581\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo - 前端也能建置部落格！佈署篇 - iT 邦幫忙::一起幫忙解決難題，拯救 IT 人的一天</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","categories":["網頁程式設計","Hexo"],"tags":["hexo","gitpage","node.js","blog"]},{"title":"HTML 基本語法","url":"/posts/31d3401f.html","content":"<img src=\"/posts/31d3401f/Html.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"開始之前\"><a href=\"#開始之前\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"開始之前\"></a>開始之前</h2><p>請先找到適合自己的編輯器。<br><code>e.g. Visual Studio Code、Sublime、Atom etc.</code></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"基本架構\"><a href=\"#基本架構\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基本架構\"></a>基本架構</h2><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      \t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">meta</span> <span class=\"attr\">charset</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"utf-8\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      \t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">title</span>&gt;</span>標題<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  \t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      \t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">          \tHello World!</span><br><span class=\"line\">      \t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  \t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"各種標籤\"><a href=\"#各種標籤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"各種標籤\"></a>各種標籤</h2><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">* <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">* <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">* <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">meta</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">* <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">* <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">* <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">* <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">**待補**</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"參考\"><a href=\"#參考\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"參考\"></a>參考</h2>","categories":["網頁程式設計","Html"],"tags":["html"]},{"title":"Markdown 常用語法","url":"/posts/c9695a23.html","content":"<img src=\"/posts/c9695a23/Markdown.png\" class=\"\">\n\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Markdown Cheatsheet</span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">  斜體： *斜體* </span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">  粗體： **粗體** </span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">  粗斜體： ***粗斜體*** </span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">  刪除線：~~刪除~~ </span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">  引言： &gt; 引言 </span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">  章節： # 章節</span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">  次級章節（以此類推）： ## 次級章節</span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">  表格（註1）：|一行|一行|疊|</span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">  插入超連結： [超連結文字](網址) </span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">  插入外部圖片： ![圖片描述](圖片網址)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["網頁程式設計","Markdown"],"tags":["Markdown"]},{"title":"UVA 272","url":"/posts/8cc8ec09.html","content":"<img src=\"/posts/8cc8ec09/UVA.png\" class=\"\">\n<h1 id=\"UVA272\"><a href=\"#UVA272\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"UVA272\"></a>UVA272</h1><a id=\"more\"></a>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"題目\"><a href=\"#題目\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"題目\"></a>題目</h2><p><a href=\"http://luckycat.kshs.kh.edu.tw/homework/q272.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">LuckyCat中文題目</a><br><a href=\"https://onlinejudge.org/index.php?option=com_onlinejudge&Itemid=8&category=4&page=show_problem&problem=208\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">UVA 272</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"解法\"><a href=\"#解法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解法\"></a>解法</h2><p>輸入一行資料並儲存，再使用for及if做條件判斷，最後印出結果。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"我的程式碼\"><a href=\"#我的程式碼\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"我的程式碼\"></a>我的程式碼</h2><figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;stdlib.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;string.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> choice = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">char</span> str[<span class=\"number\">9999</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(fgets(str,<span class=\"keyword\">sizeof</span>(str),<span class=\"built_in\">stdin</span>))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;i&lt;<span class=\"built_in\">strlen</span>(str)<span class=\"number\">-1</span>;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(str[i] == <span class=\"string\">'\"'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t(choice == <span class=\"number\">0</span>) ? (<span class=\"built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"``\"</span>),choice = <span class=\"number\">1</span>) : (<span class=\"built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"''\"</span>),choice = <span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">else</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t<span class=\"built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"%c\"</span>,str[i]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"\\n\"</span>);\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["程式練習","UVA"],"tags":["C","Computer science","UVA"]},{"title":"Welcome My Website！","url":"/posts/de228b21.html","content":"<img src=\"/posts/de228b21/Welcome.png\" class=\"\">","categories":["自我介紹"],"tags":["Profile","Outline"]}]